---
const pillars = [
  {
    n: '01',
    title: 'Ship.',
    body: 'Frontier models are easy to demo and hard to ship. I try to spend most of my time in the boring middle—evals, edge cases, latency, fallbacks—because that\'s usually where AI products earn (or lose) their keep.',
  },
  {
    n: '02',
    title: 'Trust.',
    body: 'Trust feels less like a feature and more like a side effect of small, honest decisions. I try to design for the moment someone asks "why did it do that?"—and make sure there\'s a real answer nearby.',
  },
  {
    n: '03',
    title: 'Transparency.',
    body: 'Black-box agents tend to be a short-term win. Where I can, I lean toward systems that expose their reasoning, tools, and state—so teams can debug them, users can correct them, and I can sleep at night.',
  },
];
---

<section class="manifesto" id="approach">
  <div class="wrap manifesto__inner">
    <div class="manifesto__head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Approach</span>
      <h2 class="manifesto__title">
        A few things I keep coming back to when <span class="serif-italic">building with AI.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <ol class="manifesto__list">
      {pillars.map((p) => (
        <li class="manifesto__item reveal">
          <div class="manifesto__num">{p.n}</div>
          <div class="manifesto__content">
            <h3 class="manifesto__heading">{p.title}</h3>
            <p class="manifesto__body">{p.body}</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 9vw, 9rem) 0;
  }

  .manifesto__head {
    max-width: 30ch;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.4rem;
  }

  .manifesto__title {
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .manifesto__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .manifesto__item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .manifesto__item:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .manifesto__item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .manifesto__num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .manifesto__heading {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', ui-serif, Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .manifesto__body {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
